    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, complete with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the sought-after Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service, ensuring the structural integrity of the chassis under high lateral loads. The suspension remains firm with refreshed bushings, providing the tactile feedback and turn-in precision expected of the M-division. While the aesthetics reflect a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain and longitudinal dynamics are in excellent functional order.",
