      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss luster, with only minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch, both of which are barely noticeable from a distance. The interior is smoke-free and clean; the premium upholstery is intact, showing only light softening on the driver's side bolster. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the heated seats and navigation system, is in full working order. Mechanically, this car is sound\u2014the engine pulls strongly, the transmission shifts smoothly, and there are no warning lights on the dash. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection completed just last month. The tires are matching set with plenty of life left. This is a dependable, high-quality vehicle ready for its next owner.",
